pepe the bull ( spanish : pepe el toro ) is a 1953 mexican sports drama film directed by ismael rodríguez and starring pedro infante , evita muñoz ' &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ' and amanda del &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it was the last in a trilogy of films featuring infante 's character who had first appeared in we the poor ( 1948 ) . a planned fourth film in the series was cancelled following the actor 's death . the film was nominated for three ariel awards .